Well, sir, the Lord provided such a man...

97
00:12:14,013 --> 00:12:15,310
现在我便在这里
...and here I am.

98
00:12:15,449 --> 00:12:18,317
他根本就是唬你的 哈维先生
He ain't told you one word of truth, Mr. Harvey.

99
00:12:18,454 --> 00:12:20,218
我们的农场是全镇最棒的
We had the best farm in the township.

100
00:12:20,290 --> 00:12:22,555
是啊，整个“石头村”里最棒的 全都是石头！
Yeah, Rockville Township it was. Stone County.

101
00:12:22,627 --> 00:12:24,060
喔，才不是呢！
Oh, it was not.

102
00:12:24,429 --> 00:12:26,990
是他不安于室 才把我们一家子拖到这里
It was his itchin' foot that brought us here.

103
00:12:27,334 --> 00:12:29,530
